{"tid":2208613,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有玩過GBA哈姆太郎3戀愛大冒險？","createTime":"2020-09-19T05:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T18:36:50.000Z","uid":64694,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f424f8d29fc7a7bb0355ffad4c134cb88a552036","tid":2208613,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"以前細過有玩，不過係日文版，玩到中間卡住咗玩唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前呢類game冇咩攻略，前一排睇youtube見到原來當時有出英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 英文名叫Hamtaro: Ham Ham Heartbreak<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢隻哈姆太郎3係哈姆太郎系列入面畫面做得最好最靚最好玩嘅一隻，睇返前兩集，只係整好個系統，但係畫面唔靚，後面第四集感覺都係冇咁好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一集個樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGcxv8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGcxv8c.jpg&h=c9d74c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EkvhOe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EkvhOe.jpg&h=2f400e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二集個樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FztdfAO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFztdfAO.jpg&h=4e82fe3e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1SnBdnu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1SnBdnu.png&h=4de03c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢啲哈姆太郎動作好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始就已經有隻分化撚出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2P4nec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2P4nec.jpg&h=d4f740c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JBaZVzf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJBaZVzf.jpg&h=f5040eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KOz74sD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKOz74sD.jpg&h=0b0f1a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDv7j01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDv7j01.jpg&h=576de74d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/173XHeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F173XHeo.jpg&h=2af51350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7WRMF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7WRMF4.jpg&h=a24553ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtRuyk5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtRuyk5.jpg&h=9cbd65dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uXdZ06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uXdZ06.jpg&h=25a1d0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K-aggzr_fqQ&amp;ab_channel=PikaspreyBlue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK-aggzr_fqQ%26ab_channel%3DPikaspreyBlue&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=ab6a83bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K-aggzr_fqQ&amp;ab_channel=PikaspreyBlue</a>"},{"pid":"f626fe2b75e3b4e1bd72cc507cfc22f489351d5c","tid":2208613,"uid":83640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"記得有集係要儲d人仔<br />\n叫佢地番去一齊住"},{"pid":"9753607e7a63366842059fe25b8f67ad7c19ea69","tid":2208613,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f626fe2b75e3b4e1bd72cc507cfc22f489351d5c","tid":2208613,"uid":83640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"記得有集係要儲d人仔<br />\n叫佢地番去一齊住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nheThqq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/